author: Warhammer
description:
Haughty High Elf Realms elites, lords, and soaring steeds arrive to humble their enemies in Warhammer: The Old World with next week's pre-orders, along with fresh releases for Necromunda and The Horus Heresy.

Plus, experience the nightmare of a Genestealer Cult uprising from a safe distance on Loremasters, along with two other shows arriving on Warhammer TV on Wednesday.
